    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在长期没有工作的情况下，杰克被迫加入他从小就不喜欢的家族企业。他开始了他的第一个案子，表面上很简单，但却突然变成了他最糟糕的噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与杰克-福尔摩斯一起踏上一个由活人木偶、失控的动画片和更多噩梦般的生物组成的恐怖故事，穿越诸如儿童被实验的房子、充满巨大蜘蛛的矿井和一个可怕的游乐园等奇怪的地方，你要尽一切努力求得生存。你还必须管理你找到的子弹和急救箱......哦，别忘了乘坐游乐设施</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你将面临大量的威胁</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清空敌人的弹夹，同时尽一切努力生存！你将面临各种类型的敌人！你将面临各种类型的敌人，他们有不同的机械，甚至是老板--在这里你无法逃避或躲避任何人！你将面临各种类型的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/e113542d342e6d84201ab3502ebca7ac.poster.avif?t=1768952010\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/e113542d342e6d84201ab3502ebca7ac.webm?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/e113542d342e6d84201ab3502ebca7ac.mp4?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样性和独特的场景</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗和恐怖的地点，废弃的房子，对儿童进行实验的地下室，废弃的老矿井，甚至还有一个游乐园，你可以按照自己的节奏去探索每一个角落，寻找弹药和生存工具。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/a1a96baeefa204bd778261b4f1186d2a.poster.avif?t=1768952010\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/a1a96baeefa204bd778261b4f1186d2a.webm?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/a1a96baeefa204bd778261b4f1186d2a.mp4?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个可以乘坐游乐设施的集市!  探索公园的每个部分都有其独特的氛围，并享受所有的游乐设施。但不要害怕，每个角落都潜伏着危险。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/e5e6fefdfde31cdf3650e42c042846a7.poster.avif?t=1768952010\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/e5e6fefdfde31cdf3650e42c042846a7.webm?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/e5e6fefdfde31cdf3650e42c042846a7.mp4?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> 。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>乘坐过山车!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/0b1de5cb8a5aa4486b2e01280c434dd2.poster.avif?t=1768952010\" width=780 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/0b1de5cb8a5aa4486b2e01280c434dd2.webm?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/0b1de5cb8a5aa4486b2e01280c434dd2.mp4?t=1768952010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你敢吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>壮观的图形得益于虚幻引擎4 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带有弹药和医疗包管理的FPS生存恐怖游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在安全区随时保存点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种不同的场景</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种类型的敌人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>悲惨和恐怖的故事情节</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏长度4至5小时</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235820/extras/41880029aa591352c56fa39b3e769f81.avif?t=1768952010\" width=638 height=804 /></span></p>",
